416
00:20:23,599 --> 00:20:28,480
or see a signal that is safe to enter the city.

417
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:30,559
I would like to roll a perception check

418
00:20:30,559 --> 00:20:34,400
to see what Thea's reaction to him taking his armor off is.

419
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:41,279
What's Thea's reaction to him taking his armor off?

420
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:44,400
She sings inappropriately,

421
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:51,839
and he says, all right, guys, let's go in through the sewers.

422
00:20:51,839 --> 00:20:55,039
And he leads you to the south of the city,

423
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:56,079
where the river is,

424
00:20:56,960 --> 00:21:01,200
