00:21:05,839 --> 00:21:08,240
and Flint and Hammerstriker,

429
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:10,720
they are able to walk through quite well,

430
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:14,799
but Thea and Nularaaaa, you gotta duck a little bit.

431
00:21:14,799 --> 00:21:15,839
I complain about it.

432
00:21:15,839 --> 00:21:17,679
Well, you're quite tall, aren't you, Thea?

433
00:21:17,679 --> 00:21:19,919
I'm almost six feet tall.

434
00:21:19,919 --> 00:21:21,039
That is quite tall.

435
00:21:21,039 --> 00:21:23,359
And he says to you, he's like,

436
00:21:23,359 --> 00:21:26,959
so where are you getting this armor from?

437
00:21:28,559 --> 00:21:33,359
The guy in the shopping district?

438
00:21:34,159 --> 00:21:35,279
This is the day they realize

439
00:21:35,279 --> 00:21:37,839
