440
00:21:39,119 --> 00:21:42,559
He has an underground entrance as well.

441
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:46,159
The entire city of Mirabar has an underground entrance,

442
00:21:46,159 --> 00:21:49,519
but there are two blacksmiths of decent quality,

443
00:21:49,519 --> 00:21:52,159
because this sewer will tie into those tunnels,

444
00:21:52,159 --> 00:21:54,159
and we can probably go check them out.

445
00:21:54,159 --> 00:21:56,319
Well, this blacksmith had a bunch of kids,

446
00:21:56,319 --> 00:21:57,599
