447
00:21:57,599 --> 00:21:58,720
Oh, Patrick.

448
00:21:58,720 --> 00:21:59,679
Then we'll go see him.

449
00:22:00,319 --> 00:22:00,819
Yeah.

450
00:22:01,679 --> 00:22:04,000
So you travel through the sewers,

451
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:07,519
and you don't see or hear some ruckus above,

452
00:22:07,519 --> 00:22:08,879
from the streets above,

453
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:12,640
but you come to a side tunnel

454
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:16,320
