455
00:22:16,320 --> 00:22:18,160
Mirabar tunnel network

456
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,440
that you had been in previously

457
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:20,800
when escaping the dragon.

458
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:21,760
It takes a little while,

459
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:26,240
but you get to the same blacksmith entrance

460
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,680
that you were at before.

461
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:28,960
Hammer Stryker goes up

462
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:31,200
