463
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:36,480
He kind of gives you the wait a second hand signal,

464
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,920
and he sneaks in.

465
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:40,560
You hear some shuffling about,

466
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,400
and then he comes back and waves you up,

467
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:44,320
and you walk into the blacksmith,

468
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:46,240
and it looks like it's been turned over,

469
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:48,640
like everything is knocked off the walls.

470
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,140
No.

471
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:52,720
And...

472
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:53,220
No!

473
00:22:55,279 --> 00:22:57,360
Thank you for reacting appropriately.

474
00:22:57,360 --> 00:22:59,039
Sorry, everyone else got to do it,

475
00:22:59,039 --> 00:23:00,080
so I wanted to get in on the fly.

476
00:23:00,080 --> 00:23:01,360
Well, he was real nice,

477
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,600
and I just feel bad.

478
00:23:03,600 --> 00:23:05,200
Made it through the dragon attack,

479
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:07,759
and now this dumb soldier has probably attacked him.

480
00:23:07,759 --> 00:23:10,640
Under the spell of this primsbane bastard.

481
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:14,079
I start sifting through the remaining things,

482
00:23:14,079 --> 00:23:15,759
trying to find maybe the armor,

483
00:23:15,759 --> 00:23:17,519
because I asked them for it to be fancy.

484
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:19,759
Are you trying to be quiet when you do this,

485
00:23:19,759 --> 00:23:21,519
