486
00:23:21,519 --> 00:23:22,160
No, I'm trying...

487
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:24,000
Well, first, I'm just looking around,

488
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:25,440
but if I do move anything,

489
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,799
I would like to be quiet about it.

490
00:23:26,799 --> 00:23:28,240
Should I make a stealth check?

491
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,359
How about first we say...

492
00:23:30,879 --> 00:23:32,240
Hail, Patrick!

493
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:34,319
Rather than just walking in

494
00:23:34,319 --> 00:23:36,879
and digging through the piles of rubble.

495
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:37,680
Thea's high.

496
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:38,640
Thea don't care.

497
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:39,760
Oh, you're right, you're right.

498
00:23:39,760 --> 00:23:40,400
Thea don't care.

499
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:45,040
Thea goes in and starts just rummaging through things.

500
00:23:45,040 --> 00:23:47,920
Very quietly she starts rummaging through things,

501
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:49,600
because you got a good stealth check there.

502
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:52,320
But Nularaaaa, you do yell out,

503
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:57,680
and you hear from a side room,

504
00:23:58,640 --> 00:24:01,280
you hear kind of a stir,

505
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:04,880
and like a picking up of a sword and shield,

506
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:05,600
and you hear...

507
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:08,240
Who? Who's there?

508
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:08,800
Patty!

509
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:10,800
Oh, it's you.

510
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:13,520
Did you bring the army, too?

511
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:14,480
You brought the dragon.

512
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,760
Did you bring the army?

513
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:19,120
And he kind of slowly walks out of this back room.

514
00:24:19,120 --> 00:24:22,480
Looks like he's been in a bit of a battle,

515
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:24,480
but he looks okay.

516
00:24:24,480 --> 00:24:26,640
Just looks like he's been roughed up a little bit.

517
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:30,400
Do he and Hammerstriker embrace or anything?

518
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:31,280
They know each other?

519
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:33,360
Do they kiss on the mouth?

520
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:33,840
Hammerstriker...

521
00:24:33,839 --> 00:24:35,359
Do they kiss on the mouth?

522
00:24:35,359 --> 00:24:37,039
...was clearing another room,

523
00:24:37,039 --> 00:24:39,919
but he walks in at the same time,

524
00:24:39,919 --> 00:24:42,959
and they don't kiss on the mouth.

525
00:24:44,319 --> 00:24:45,439
They acknowledge each other,

526
00:24:45,439 --> 00:24:48,720
and Hammerstriker asks him if he's okay,

527
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:51,119
